# Dynamic API keys {% #dynamic-api-keys %}

You can use headers like dynamic API keys in your function, which give you access to your project services and allow you to operate without sessions. To configure your dynamic API key scopes, modify the scopes in the `appwrite.json` file. To apply those configured scopes to your function in the Console, push your function using `appwrite push functions`.

